00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:42.400
Maybe this density matrix goes
through the next beam splitter

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:44.510
and then we want to know
what comes out of it.

00:08:44.510 --> 00:08:47.950
And all we have to
apply is the formalism

00:08:47.950 --> 00:08:52.680
we developed for the beam
splitter earlier in the course.

00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:55.750
Of course, the beam
