the vacuum, is 0.

00:14:19.430 --> 00:14:25.096
Well, look a few weeks
back, we have done that all.

00:14:25.096 --> 00:14:32.360
The output state is, well,
there was a probability, alpha,

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:38.410
that we had no photon
in the state psi.

00:14:38.410 --> 00:14:40.340
And if we have no
