00:27:49.540 --> 00:27:56.120
and there are no correlations
from here to here to here,

00:27:56.120 --> 00:27:57.990
there is no memory effect.

00:27:57.990 --> 00:27:59.690
Everything is
completely uncorrelated.

00:28:07.340 --> 00:28:10.240
So the environment
