00:28:28.390 --> 00:28:31.040
So these are the two
effects which are important.

00:28:31.040 --> 00:28:33.820
One is no memory
for the environment,

00:28:33.820 --> 00:28:37.020
Delta function correlation,
Markov approximation,

00:28:37.020 --> 00:28:40.290
and the two, of
course, are related

00:28:40.290 --> 00:28:42.680
in the environment is all
of this in the same state.

