00:30:25.050 --> 00:30:26.480
state.

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:30.940
This equation would say that
the excited state decays

00:30:30.940 --> 00:30:35.620
with the rate gamma,
and sometimes you

00:30:35.620 --> 00:30:38.430
