00:42:13.430 --> 00:42:16.120
splitter, how they
are now implemented

00:42:16.120 --> 00:42:18.520
in a very general context.

00:42:18.520 --> 00:42:23.890
I will not be able to give you
all of the mathematical aspects

00:42:23.890 --> 00:42:27.920
of it, but I think by now you
