01:07:48.850 --> 01:07:52.100
It's not changed by the
interaction with the system.

01:07:52.100 --> 01:07:53.820
And this is the
Bohr approximation.

01:07:53.820 --> 01:07:58.650
We just use the same expression
for the reservoir independent

01:07:58.650 --> 01:08:00.610
of the measurements
the reservoir has done.

